## Why This Is Asked

Tests mastery of modern CSS layout: two-pane grids, CSS-only UI state (no JS), and production-friendly animation with accessibility in mind. It also checks how candidates balance visual polish with stability at scale.

## Key Concepts

- CSS Grid two-pane layouts with responsive breakpoints
- CSS-only toggle for mobile collapsible rail
- grid-auto-columns and minmax for fluid card grids
- subtle entrance animations with stagger and motion preferences
