## Why This Is Asked
Tests fundamental Flexbox understanding and practical layout skills that are essential for frontend development at HRT.

## Expected Answer
Candidate should explain justify-content: space-between distributes outer items to edges, then discuss centering the middle item using margin: 0 auto or flex: 1 with text-align: center.

